      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 55.11</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>心使氣曰強。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When things have become strong, they (then) become old, which may be said to be contrary to the Dao.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
