      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 55.12</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>物壯則老，謂之不道，不道早已。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Whatever is contrary to the Dao soon ends.</seg>
      </tuv>
